articles.contents:
About Me
I am a recent graduate from the University of Nebraska - Lincoln with
a Bachelor of Arts in Economics and Mathematics. I have previously
worked as:
Economic Research Analyst @ Bureau of Business Research.
Data Analyst Intern @ Institute of Agriculture and Natural
Resources.
Research Assistant @ Department of Economics, University of
Nebraska - Lincoln.
